title: US OPEN RECAP, A WEEK OF MAYHEM
description:
The entire surf world flocks to Huntington Beach, California to participate in the world's largest surf festival. Fox team riders Damien Hobgood, Bede Durbidge, Keanu Asing, and Ian Walsh showed up and blew up.
They were on hand to sign autographs for crazed fans and watch the world premiere of Fox's latest surf film #NOFILTER.
